2015-06-04 13:41:05	DarkRedeemer	Then wrap those in properties.
2015-06-04 13:41:46	DarkRedeemer	public int Var1 { get { return _var1; } set { _var1 = value; } }
2015-06-04 13:41:55	DarkRedeemer	same for Var2.
